Well...

324
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:14,500
The next time she comes in, you be sure to send her to my office.

325
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:17,840
You betcha.

326
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:24,970
Gee, I wish my daddy owned a bank.

327
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:28,390
