449
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,720
Somebody hit the joint before we could.

450
00:41:13,970 --> 00:41:16,300
Here, Doc.

451
00:41:16,430 --> 00:41:18,810
Here you go, buddy.
Suck on that.

452
00:41:24,100 --> 00:41:25,850
Son of a bitch!

453
00:41:28,230 --> 00:41:31,070
